title: NDFD NOAA, Wind speed/direction forecast after Gustav landfall along Louisiana coast Sep 03, 2008, USA, Aug 30, 2008
name: NDFD NOAA, Wind speed/direction forecast after Gustav landfall along Louisiana coast Sep 03, 2008, USA, Aug 30, 2008
description:
The point shapefile shows the forecast for wind speed and direction along Lousiana coast line on Sep 03, 2008 after Gustav makes a landfall on 2nd Sept, 2008. The shapefile was generated from 7-day gridded forecasts by NDFD
 (National Digital Forecast Database)as of Aug 30, 2008 for the lower mississippi valley
